              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "model": {
                  "text": "David Davis's Brexit department will also warn the scheme could cost the EU an extra €1bn (£876m) without the UK's continued involvement. ",
                  "blocks": [
                    {
                      "type": "fragment",
